It's been 14 years since the bomb destroyed New York and super humans disappeared. But, no longer! A new age is beginning! A new generation to right the wrongs of the old!

They are: Feather! Atomic-X! Galvanic! Dreamscape! and the mysterious D, the Phantom Cowl!

To uphold the legacy of Earth's Greatest Heroes, they fight the forces of evil as... the ALL-NEW UNION!
